  - id: butler
    displayName: "Desir\xE9e Cahu\xE8te"
    portrait: {fileID: 7142518519572273488, guid: ad514fb12feb06641907c05812225daf, type: 3}
    isLeftSide: 0
    neutral: {fileID: -7806103805540087679, guid: 6c89d086796f9134f9345d60908d642e, type: 3}
    happy: {fileID: 0}
    sad: {fileID: 0}
    angry: {fileID: 0}
    surprised: {fileID: 0}
    thinking: {fileID: 0}
  nodes:
  - id: start
    speakerID: butler
    text: "\u266A Oh, mistress Vivienne\u2026 Your voice was more beautiful than
      the angels\u2019\u2026 \u266A"
    nextNodeID: start
    choices:
    - text: Excuse me?
      nextNodeID: 1
      addFlags: []
      requiredFlags: []
      onSelectedEvent: {fileID: 0}
      endsDialogue: 0
    - text: See you
      nextNodeID: 
      addFlags: []
      requiredFlags: []
      onSelectedEvent: {fileID: 0}
      endsDialogue: 1
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 0
  - id: 1
    speakerID: butler
    text: "Hm?\nOh\u2026 you\u2019re not her.\n\u2026Sorry."
    nextNodeID: 1
    choices:
    - text: "I\u2019m Lyra. I\u2019m trying to understand what happened to Vivienne."
      nextNodeID: 2
      addFlags: []
      requiredFlags: []
      onSelectedEvent: {fileID: 0}
      endsDialogue: 0
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 0
  - id: 2
    speakerID: butler
    text: "Ah\u2026 my lady\u2026 Still radiant. Even now."
    nextNodeID: 2
    choices:
    - text: You cared about her a lot.
      nextNodeID: 3
      addFlags: []
      requiredFlags: []
      onSelectedEvent: {fileID: 0}
      endsDialogue: 0
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 0
  - id: 3
    speakerID: butler
    text: "More than anything. Well\u2026 perhaps equally to peanuts."
    nextNodeID: 3
    choices:
    - text: "You were there the night she died, weren\u2019t you?"
      nextNodeID: 4
      addFlags: []
      requiredFlags: []
      onSelectedEvent: {fileID: 0}
      endsDialogue: 0
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 1
    expression: 0
  - id: 4
    speakerID: butler
    text: But Lady Vivienne was allergic, so I learned restraint.
    nextNodeID: 5
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 1
    expression: 0
  - id: 5
    speakerID: butler
    text: Yes.
    nextNodeID: 5
    choices:
    - text: What happened?
      nextNodeID: 6
      addFlags: []
      requiredFlags: []
      onSelectedEvent: {fileID: 0}
      endsDialogue: 0
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 0
  - id: 6
    speakerID: butler
    text: "The manor was full of guests. A grand celebration, all for her final performance.
      She left during a short intermission before the last song\u2026 and never came
      back."
    nextNodeID: 7
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 1
    expression: 0
  - id: 7
    speakerID: butler
    text: "Laurent went looking for her first. Then\u2026 the screaming started."
    nextNodeID: 7
    choices:
    - text: Did you notice anything strange before that?
      nextNodeID: 8
      addFlags: []
      requiredFlags: []
      onSelectedEvent: {fileID: 0}
      endsDialogue: 0
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 1
    expression: 0
  - id: 8
    speakerID: butler
    text: "Lady Vivienne was frightened lately. She believed people around her wished
      her harm. \u2026But I would never let anything happen to her. "
    nextNodeID: 9
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 1
    expression: 0
  - id: 9
    speakerID: butler
    text: NEVER.
    nextNodeID: 
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
